metadata.name: BUSANZA
metadata.description:
Inspired by Fidenza or vice versa? Busan's Gamcheon Culture Village is real-life Tyler Hobbs' Fidenza situated in the southern city in South Korea. This area is known for its layered streets, twisted alleys, brightly painted houses, inspiring tourists to explore. 

This is an open edition for the people. Enjoy, collect, gift. 

Artist: Ev Tchebotarev
Title: Busanza
Format: JPG
Year: 2018
Coordinates: 35° 5' 57" N 129° 0' 50" E
Camera: DJI
Dimensions: 2000x3000px
